{
  "stem": "58.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It went through the skin, the skin, the bullet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I tear off a piece of my shirt and I tied it around.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I held him up, and we walked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We walked away, and we saw a village.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We walked into the village, and I told them my father was shot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they gave me some real gauze, one lace around.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I cleaned it out, and asked for some iodine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I figured at least it wouldn't get infected.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I put some iodine and I tied it around.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I made him like a crutch, you know, to be able to walk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And it took us about seven, eight days to walk home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Because the roads were crowded with, with army units, going back and forth, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And you also had to walk not on the main road, because you were afraid you're going to be picked up for work.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "That's what some did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They came to Lodz, and some people were picked up and held for weeks for work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "When they came home they told us-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we came, we came home-- it was about the time of Sukkot, you know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "The city was deserted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "There was a-- they were already taking people to work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Well, when we came home, we couldn't recognize the city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "My parents-- first of all, they confiscated everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They told us to get out of the orchards, they took whatever they wanted.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They took over the whole ranch, with everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Horses, wagons, they needed everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But also the family came to the city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Came to the city, they started taking people to work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "The first work I encountered was they took me to spread manure with my hands.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "This was like [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not considered work.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
